<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" class="no-js">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<title>Troll For Humanity</title>
	<style>

		body, html {
			background-color: black;
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
			overflow: hidden;
		}

		header {
			background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
			border-radius: 25px;
			color: #FFF;
			padding: 20px 40px;
			position: absolute;
			top: 30%;
			right: -2%;
			text-align: center;
			width: 50%;
		}

		header > p, header > h1 {
			margin-top: 30px;
			width: 80%;
		}

		img {
			width: 100%;
		}

		section {
			overflow: hidden;
		}

		.butt-butt {
			border-radius: 5px;
			background-color: #77DDAA;
			color: white;
			font-size: 1.6em;
			font-weight: 800;
			padding: 10px 20px;
			margin-top: 0px;
			text-decoration: none;
		}

		.heart-shaped-box {
			max-width: 100%;
			max-height: 100%;
			overflow: hidden;
		}

	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<header>
		<h1>Thank you!</h1>
		<p>
			Raising awareness of what cyber-bullying looks like is the first step to facing it together.
			Feel free to reach out to us on Twitter at <strong style="color: #FFAADD">@tfhoutreach</strong>
			to tell us about your experience and help to spread the word.
		</p>
		<p>
			<a href="/" class="butt-butt">Start Another Campaign</a>
		</p>
	</header>

	<section id="cd-timeline" class="cd-container">
		<div class="heart-shaped-box">
			<img src="/img/heart.jpg">
		</div>
	</section> <!-- cd-timeline -->
</body>
</html>
